Class ParameterList

java.lang.Object
  de.fhg.fokus.restac.httpx.core.common.ParameterList

public class ParameterList
extends java.lang.Object

Name-value pairs which contain the query of the request. Parameters in the query without value are saved as name with value null.

Author:
Murat Ates
